WEBVTT

06:24.090 --> 06:26.830 line:80%
Someone reported movement
on the mountain outside the city.

06:26.830 --> 06:27.880 line:80%
Magistrate has sent people

06:27.880 --> 06:28.930 line:80%
-to search the mountain.
-I'll go find them.

06:28.930 --> 06:30.390 line:80%
You can't go out right now.

06:30.610 --> 06:33.770 line:80%
-The magistrate didn't let you go home.
-My parents are dead.
